<h2>Mozilla IoT</h2>
<span><p>
These cards show how to connect MicroBlocks projects to the internet using Mozilla's free,
open-source WebThing Gateway software running on a Raspberry Pi. This allows users to interact
securely with MicroBlocks projects using any web browser–even from their phone!
</p></span>

<ul class="list">
    <li>
    	<a href="cards/WOT_WebLight.pdf">Web Light</a>
